  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have started to develop Diplomacy beyond other skills, delving deeper into its possibilities.</p><p><strong>Core Feats</strong></p><ul><li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.0GF2j54roPFIDmXf]{Bon Mot}</li></ul><p>Choose one Skill Path and gain that path's Trained feat.</p><p><strong>Available Skill Paths</strong></p><ul><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.AHCnDEptOM5CZyME]{Favors Path - Trained}</strong>: You know how to charm people into doing whatever you ask of them.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.MOSkpWQuc4SvXifm]{Rhetoric Path - Trained}</strong>: You have mastered the ability to impress people with words alone.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.thvXwYPDCnm4KG4C]{Connections Path - Trained}</strong>: You are excellent in exploiting your contacts for whatever information you need.</li></ul>",
